<div id="setup">
	<h2>Setting up your Jetpack</h2>
	<h2>Step 1 - Activating your Jetpack</h2>
		<p>
			<tmpl_var _("webui", "help_setup_step1_text")>
		</p>

	<h2>Step 2 – Connecting Devices to your Jetpack’s Wi-Fi Network</h2>
		<p>Tap <strong>Wi-Fi Name/Password</strong> on the <tmpl_var _("webui", "webui_product_name_with_suffix")> screen to see the Primary Wi-Fi network’s name and password. Swipe to see the Guest network’s name and password.
		</p>	
		<p>
			On your Wi-Fi enabled device, find the network you want to connect to on the list of available networks and enter the password when prompted.
		</p>
		<p>
			Note: For added security, share the Guest network with other users.
		</p>		
